  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: A transaction can't be singed while device is offline. Nothing changes when \"Sign transaction\" button is clicked. After some time, \"context deadline exceeded\" error appears. \r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/40186696-09566042-59f6-11e8-92d3-29d0e215f901.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7532782/40186705-1056f190-59f6-11e8-989b-bdb62f54e4cd.png\" width=\"200\">\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTransaction is signed and sent as soon as possible.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nTransaction is not signed. The app does not react when \"Sign transaction\" is pressed. An error with technical description appears.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go offline\r\n- Go to Wallet and try to send transaction\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly, May 16\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
